description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment of site to provide a mixture of self contained and supported persons units comprising 2 1/2 storey block to provide a 6 bed residential care home, a three storey block of 7 supported flats with associated communal areas, 5 blocks of 3 and 4 storeys comprising a total of 17 one bed and 52 two bed flats, with associated parking, landscaping and access.
